Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=46}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.96,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Rękę ma chociaż całą?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:34.47,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{If he back off even a step,\Nit would've been bitten off! - OG}{If he backed off even a step,\Nhe would've lost that arm! - Gaijin}Dobrze, że stał w miejscu,\Nbo inaczej by ją stracił!{Polly - Usopp and Gen can't really hear each other here so he probably would say "arm", but for the benefit of the audience it sounds better this way; alternatively, maybe we can just make Usopp's previously line read more like "Is he okay?" even though it strays a bit}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:39.64,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{In his case, it's not that he thought\Nabout how animal's fangs work, though. - OG}{I doubt he thought too much about\Nwhat the fangs'd do to him, though. - Gaijin}{[/q2]I doubt he thought too much about\Nwhat the fangs would do to him, though. - Polly}To zwykły przypadek. On nie ma\Npojęcia, jak działają kły rekina.{LP+Polly - he does say "animal fangs" but lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:44.69,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Z ręką bracha wszystko gra?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:57.82,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Oh...? - OG}C-Co?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.12,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Gdzie go wcięło?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:02.66,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Morze!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:03.50,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Morze?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:07.42,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Rekin sobie pływa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.63,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Przecież to Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.30,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{What? Did he dive in? - OG}Co? Zanurkował?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:21.35,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{This isn't good!\NHis ability doubles in the water. - OG}{This is serious! He's twice\Nas powerful in the water. - Gaijin}{This is bad! He's twice\Nas powerful in the water! - Polly}Kicha! Przecież w wodzie\Nstaje się jeszcze silniejszy!{Gaijin+Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:29.86,Thoughts-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{No one can stop me once my\Nspeed accelerates in the water. - OG}{No one can stop me once\NI gather speed underwater. - Gaijin}Nikt nie zdoła powstrzymać\Nprędkości, którą nabiorę pod wodą.{Gaijin+Spicy}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:34.86,Thoughts-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{This is precisely an ability\Nthat is given only to fishmen. - OG}{This ability is precisely the kind\Nbestowed only to fishmen. - Gaijin}{This is exactly the kind of power\Ngranted only to fishmen. - Polly}To doskonały przykład przewagi,\Nktórą obdarzeni zostali ryboludzie.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:37.82,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Uciekł?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:46.33,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Shark... - OG}Shark on...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.67,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Darts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.92,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Co to było?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.01,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Torpeda jakaś?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.97,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Something flew out from the sea! - OG}{Something flew out of the sea! - Gaijin}Coś wystrzeliło z wody!{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:08.39,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Auć...! Auć, auć, auć, auć...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.69,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{I'm impressed you dodged it. - OG}{You handled that well. - Gaijin}Jestem pod wrażeniem,\Nże tego uniknąłeś.{LP}
Comment: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:16.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wow, I'm impressed you dodged it. - OG}Wow, you handled that well.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:21.70,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{But the more you dodge it,\Nthe longer your hell continues. - OG}Ale im więcej będziesz unikać,\Ntym dłużej spędzisz w piekle.{But the more you dodge,\Nthe more hell you'll get. - Gaijin}{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:28.66,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Shark Darts! - OG}Shark on Darts!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:42.64,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Wha...! What kind of bones\Ndoes that damn shark have?! - OG}T-Ten cholerny rekin\Nma kości ze stali, czy jak?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.60,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{His nose crushed the ground...! - OG}Roztrzaskał ziemię nosem!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:49.85,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Shark Darts! - OG}Shark on Darts!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:09.29,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Hey Luffy, hide!\NArlong went into the sea again! - OG}{Hey Luffy, you gotta hide!\NArlong went into the sea again! - Gaijin}Hej Luffy, schowaj się gdzieś!\NOn znowu dał nura do wody!{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.58,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Big Bro! Please hurry up and hide! - OG}{Big Bro! Please hurry and hide! - Gaijin}Brachu! Schowaj swoje cztery litery!{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.80,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{He'll target you again! - OG}Zaraz znów się na ciebie rzuci!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:21.76,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Uciekaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.76,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Nie... Nie ma mowy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.77,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Don't be stupid! Are you knowingly\Ngoing to become a target?! Hide! - OG}{Don't be stupid! Are you [/i1]trying[/i0]\Nto be a target?! Take cover! - Gaijin}{Don't be stupid! You're a sitting duck\Nlike that! Take cover! - Spicy+Polly}Zgłupiałeś do reszty?! Ma cię\Njak na widelcu! Schowaj się!{Spicy+Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:36.77,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{I don't want to! I'll catch him\Nand break his nose! - OG}Nie ma mowy! Złapię go\Ni połamię mu tego nochala!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.99,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Come on! Shark! - OG}No dajesz, rekinie!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:45.20,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Masz tupet.{OG}{You got some nerve. - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.91,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Or have you realized\Nthat it's useless to run away? - OG}{Or have you realized that running\Naway is not gonna save you? - Gaijin}{Or have you realized that running\Naway won't save you? - Gaijin+Polly}A może zdałeś sobie sprawę,\Nże ucieczka nic ci nie da?{Gaijin+Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:53.54,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Didn't you hear us saying\Nyou should hide, Luffy?! - OG}{Can't you see that you've\Ngotta hide, Luffy?! - Gaijin}Czego nie rozumiesz w zdaniu\N"pospiesz się i uciekaj"?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:57.55,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{You barely dodged his attacks,\Nand they all grazed you! - OG}{You barely dodged his attacks,\Nbut they all grazed you! - Gaijin}Ledwo uniknąłeś jego ataków!{LP+Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:06:01.47,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{If you take a direct hit, you'll die instantly! - OG}{That move will instantly kill\Nyou if you take its full force! - dan/Gaijin}Zginiesz przy bezpośrednim zderzeniu!{LP+Gordy+Spicy}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.34,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gumowa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:08.39,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tarcza!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.39,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{What's that position? - OG}{What's that stance? - Gaijin}Co to za postawa?{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.35,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Surely he isn't going to\Nstop the attack like that? - OG}{He wouldn't try to stop\Nthe attack like that, right? - Gaijin}{He's not gonna try and stop it, is he?! - Polly}{He's gonna try doing [/i1]that[/i0] to block it?! - LP}{He's not gonna use [/i1]that[/i0] to block it, is he? - LP}Chyba nie chce tego blokować?{LP}{Polly - It's like the idea that he would block it is ridiculous to begin with, but the fact that he's also using something ridiculous to DO so is even MORE ridiculous}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.31,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{This is double the acceleration\Ndistance from earlier. - OG}{I have twice the distance\Nto accelerate this time! - Gaijin}{I have twice as far\Nto pick up speed now! - Polly}Będzie dwa razy szybciej niż ostatnio!{Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.48,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{I'll pierce your heart! - OG}{I'll punch through your heart! - Gaijin}Przeszyję ci serce na wylot!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:23.11,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Shark Darts! - OG}Shark on Darts!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:30.70,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{He got hit! - OG}Trafił go!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:45.59,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{What?! Did he get hit?! - OG}Chwila! To oberwał czy nie?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.55,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{No! He flung himself off! - OG}Nie! Wystrzelił się w powietrze!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:54.48,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Przegrałeś! Ten atak więcej nie zadziała!{OG}{You're done! That attack\Nwon't work anymore! - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:58.06,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Shark Darts! - OG}Shark on Darts!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:06.20,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{You bastard! That was\Nby instinct, wasn't it?! - OG}A niech cię! To był zwykły fuks!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.91,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Pora to zakończyć!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.87,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{You won't hit me! - OG}Nic mi nie zrobisz!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.83,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gumowa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.62,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Finger Net! - OG}Sieć!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.75,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Fishing! Fishing! - OG}To jak łowienie ryb! Złowiłem rybę!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.01,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,No i...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.80,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Włócznia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.90,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Whoa! - OG}{Zoinks! - Polly}{Holy cow! - Polly}Jasny gwint!{Polly}{Gadzooks! - Z}{Egad! - Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.86,Secondary-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Tak jest! Dajesz!{LP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.07,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Hm...? Did he die? - OG}Co? Już nie żyje?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:50.49,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Oczy Arlonga się zmieniły!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:54.79,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{They look the same as the eyes that\Nsea kings show when they snap. - OG}{He looks just like\Nthe sea kings when they attack. - Gaijin}Wygląda jak Królowie Mórz,\Ngdy ktoś ich porządnie wnerwi.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:58.00,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{He must've snapped\Nwith Luffy's last attack! - OG}{Luffy's last attack must've pissed him off! - Gaijin}Atak Luffy'ego na pewno miał taki efekt!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:04.42,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{I've never seen\NArlong's eyes like that... - OG}{I've never seen Arlong\Nwith a look like that... - Gaijin}Nigdy nie widziałam\NArlonga w takim stanie...{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:07.59,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{You inferior human! - OG}Nędzny człowieku!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.51,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{What did you do... - OG}{What do you think\Nyou're doing to me?! - Gaijin}Wydaje ci się, że możesz...{Polly+LP - This line is very much grandstanding}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.22,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{to me, a fishman?! - OG}{I'm a fishman! - Gaijin}podnosić rękę na ryboludzia!?{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.32,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Boy, was I stunned! - OG}{Boy, was that a shocker! - Gaijin}{Boy, that was a shocker! - Gaijin+Polly}O chłopie, wziął mnie z zaskoczenia!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:29.28,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{It doesn't hurt but\NI can see he's really mad. - OG}Nie, żeby jakoś bolało,\Nale ewidentnie jest wkurzony.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.42,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Co tym razem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.04,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Shark Saw! - OG}{Kiribachi! - Gaijin}To Kiribachi!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:45.42,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{It's a giant saw! - OG}{That's a monster saw! - Gaijin}Przeogromna piła!{LP+Polly - And BTW Gordy also loves this line. I heard Jaz loves it too, don't ask her though}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.74,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Brachu Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.36,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Dasz radę, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:13.37,Secondary-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uciekaj! Uważaj tam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:13.37,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{The attack won't stop...\NHe's getting cornered...! - OG}{The attack is relentless.\NHe's cornered! - Gaijin}On nie da za wygraną!\NNie ma dokąd uciec!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.88,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Schował się w budynku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:33.09,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Okno po lewej na najwyższym piętrze...{OG}{It's the left window on the top floor... -Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:36.10,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{That room is... - OG}Tamten pokój...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.48,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{You can no longer escape. - OG}Nie masz dokąd uciec.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:44.15,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,To najwyższe piętro Arlong Parku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.07,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{What's this room? - OG}Co to za pokój?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.03,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Full of papers... - OG}Pełno tu kartek.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.36,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{These're not just ordinary papers. - OG}To nie byle kartki.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:54.49,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{This room is where I make that\Nwoman draw sea charts. It's... - OG}{This room is where I make that\Ngirl draw sea charts. It's... - Gaijin}Ta dziewczyna rysowała dla mnie\Nmapy właśnie tutaj. Ten pokój to...{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:57.49,Thoughts-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{The survey room! - OG}{...the survey room! - Gaijin}...pracownia kartograficzna!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:09:59.91,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Pokój Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:03.83,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{These're all sea charts\Nthat Nami drew. - OG}{These are the sea charts\Nthat Nami drew. - Gaijin}Nami narysowała każdą z tych map.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:10.97,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{How many people in this world\Ncan draw such accurate charts? - OG}{Across the globe, few could draw\Ncharts as accurate as these! - Gaijin}{Hardly anyone in the world could\Ndraw charts as accurate as these! - Polly}Jak ci się wydaje, ilu ludzi potrafi\Nrysować mapy z taką dokładnością?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.47,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{The girl has a gift. - OG}Dziewczyna ma talent.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:24.10,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{There's nothing as unfortunate and foolish - OG}Nie ma nic gorszego\Ni bardziej nędznego{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.69,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{as letting a natural-born\Ntalent go to waste. - OG}od zaprzepaszczenia\Nwrodzonego talentu.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:32.32,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Staying here and drawing sea charts\Nis the greatest happiness for her! - OG}{She'll find true happiness\Nin staying here and drawing charts! - Gaijin}Korzystanie z niego celem rysowania\Nnam map to jej szansa na szczęście!{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:36.20,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Te pióro jest pokryte krwią...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:41.41,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Nami's charts are absolutely vital\Nif I'm to attain world supremacy! - OG}Bez map rysowanych przez Nami\Nnie będę w stanie zawładnąć nad światem!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:49.42,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{She's going to continue drawing\Nsea charts! For [/i1]my[/i0] ambition! - OG}{She's going to continue drawing\Nsea charts! All for [/i1]my[/i0] ambition! - Gaijin}{That girl is going to continue drawing\Nsea charts! All for [/i1]my[/i0] ambition! - Gaijin+Polly}Nadal będzie rysować te mapy,\Ndokładając się do {\i1}mojego {\i0}celu!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:53.01,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{And once her charts give me full\Nknowledge of all the world's seas... - OG}Kiedy jej mapy objawią nam wszelkie\Ntajemnice skrywane przez morza,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:58.68,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{we fishmen will be invincible,\Nand the world will become our empire! - OG}{we fishmen will be invincible,\Nand my empire will span the globe! - Gaijin}{\q2}rasa ryboludzi zajmie wreszczie przeznaczone\N jej miejsce, a świat stanie się moim imperium!{Gaijin+LP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:04.77,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Our first stepping stone is this\Nisland... and the East Blue! - OG}{This island and the East Blue\Nare the springboards for that end! - Gaijin}Ta wyspa, a następnie East Blue\Nto tylko pierwsze kroki wyprawy!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:12.19,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Could [/i1]you[/i0] use the girl\Nas efficiently as that?! - OG}{How could you possibly use\Nher as effectively as that?! - Gaijin}Jak niby ktoś taki jak ty mógłby\Nwykorzystać ją lepiej niż ja?!{Gaijin+LP - It's more personal}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.83,Thoughts-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Huh?! The Shark Saw... - OG}{What the...?! Kiribachi... - Gaijin}Co do...?! Moje Kiribachi...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.25,Thoughts-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{won't move one bit! - OG}ani drgnie!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.21,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Jak to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.42,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,"Wykorzystać"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.76,Secondary-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{What's goin' on inside?! - OG}Co tam się dzieje?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:41.51,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Niech to... Co tam się\Nwyprawia, Brachu Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.48,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Ciężko stwierdzić, do czego tam doszło...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:49.65,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.73,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Za co ty ją uważasz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:59.07,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{An inferior creature,\Nbut a smart girl. - OG}{She's an inferior creature,\Nbut a smart girl. - Gaijin}{She's an inferior creature,\Nbut she's a smart girl, too. - Gaijin+Polly}Za podrzędny gatunek,\Nale ma chociaż głowę na karku.{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.74,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Gdyby tak zrównać ludzi ze szczurami,{OG}{If other humans were sewer rats, - dan}{If you compare all other\Nhumans to sewer rats, - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:04.70,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{I'd say she's a cheeky-as-hell cat. - OG}{she'd probably be a sassy little cat. - dan}to ona byłaby podstępnym kotkiem.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.96,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Co jak co, ale jest urocza.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:12.42,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{And I'm going to keep on feeding her\Nand buying clothes she likes. - OG}Będzie miała co żreć i dostanie\Nwszystkie ciuchy, których zechce.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:16.01,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Nie zabraknie jej niczego,\Nco potrzebne w dogodnym życiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:21.26,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{All she needs to do is keep\Ndrawing charts for me. - OG}Wystarczy tylko, że będzie rysować\Ndla mnie mapy. To jedyny warunek.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:26.39,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Już zawsze będzie moim narzędziem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.49,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.85,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{my friend. - OG}{a part of my crew. - Gaijin}{my [/i1]friend[/i0]. - LP+Polly}jedną z {\i1}nas{\i0}.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.32,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Co to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:43.49,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Biurko...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.70,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Biurko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.83,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Wh-Whew! Just a desk. - OG}F-Fiu! Na szczęście to tylko biurko.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.42,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Prawie zawału dostałem. Myślałem,\Nże to brachu Luffy poleciał...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.25,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Chwila no, partnerze mój!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:58.38,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Chyba nie mówisz, że wątpisz\Nw siłę brachola Luffy'ego?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:02.34,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Co...?! Przecież ty też\Npodskoczyłeś ze strachu, Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.35,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,G-Głupi jesteś?!\NJa po prostu, no wiesz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.81,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Tego no...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.68,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{O-Of course I thought it\Nwas that damn Arlong! - OG}{I-I naturally thought\Nit was that damn Arlong! - Gaijin}Po prostu myślałem, że to Arlong!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.77,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Huh?! That sounds kinda\Nfake if you ask me! - OG}Co?! Jak na moje to coś kręcisz!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:16.01,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)}{Say what, you jerk?! Of course\Nthere's no way Big Bro Luffy'd lose! - OG}{Say what, you jerk?! Of course,\NBig Bro Luffy'd never lose! - Gaijin}Co ty tam gadasz, kretynie?!\NTo oczywiste, że brachu Luffy nie przegra!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.36,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.70,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Co ty sobie myślisz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:26.37,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{What in the...?! There's\Nan awful lot of stuff flying! - OG}{What the hell is going on?!\NAll that random crap is flying about! - Gaijin}Co tam się dzieje?!\NWszystko wylatuje w powietrze!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:39.34,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,No dobra! Od dziś to będzie twój pokój!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.59,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Masz tu biurko, pióra...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:44.47,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Jest tu wszystko, czego\Nmogłabyś potrzebować!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.73,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Przestań!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.81,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Mapy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:56.15,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,M-Moje mapy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:00.82,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Durny bachor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.40,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Myślałaś, że dam się nabrać...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.74,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,na jakieś fałszywki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:11.21,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Nie wiedziałem, że masz czas\Nna rysowanie takich badziewi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:19.30,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Try to fool me again, and I'll drag\Npeople from the village one by one - OG}Jeszcze raz mi coś takiego odstawisz,\Nto przyprowadzę tu resztę wieśniaków,{WF+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:22.01,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{and make you watch as I crush them! - OG}{and make you watch\Nas I wring their necks! - Gaijin}a ty będziesz oglądać,\Njak giną z mojej ręki!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:23.63,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Just like I did with her! - OG}{They'll meet the same fate as her! - Gaijin}Podzielą jej los!{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.68,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Gnoju! Poświęciłem osiem\Nlat, żeby je narysowała!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:34.65,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Poświęciłem osiem lat\Nna te mapy! Na mój cel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.61,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Bell-mère{-san}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:43.57,Flashbacks-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Nojiko...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:52.29,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,To musi być zacięta walka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.83,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Tak! Wygląda na to,\Nże walczą na śmierć i życie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:55.79,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Jak nic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:05.63,Thoughts-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Dziękuję...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:14.89,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{You've gone too far,\Nyou damn rubber man! - OG}Srogo przesadziłeś, gumowy imbecylu!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.69,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{"Fishmen are great" and... - OG}"Ryboludzie są lepsi"...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.40,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,"Mapy morskie" to,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.61,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,"Szanse" tamto...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:25.95,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Niewiele wiem o takich rzeczach...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:30.78,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,ale wiem co zrobić, żeby jej pomóc!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:39.63,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{She can't go because\Nthis room is here! - OG}To właśnie przez ten pokój\Nnie mogła odejść!{Gaijin}
Comment: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:44.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If she doesn't want to be here,\Nthen I'll just destroy it all! - OG}{She doesn't want to be here,\Nso I'll just destroy it all! - Gaijin}It's not a home, it's a prison cell!{Polly} {If she doesn't want to be here,\Nthen I'll just destroy it all! - OG}{She doesn't want to be here,\Nso I'll just destroy it all! - Gaijin}I'm gonna smash it to smithereens!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.25,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{If she doesn't want to be here,\Nthen I'll just destroy it all! - OG}{She doesn't want to be here,\Nso I'll just destroy it all! - Gaijin}To żaden dom. To jej więzienie!{Nikki}{Polly - A bunch of TLs chimed in on this one; He's using the word 居場所 which is specifically like a "place one belongs", or like the English concept of a "home" rather than a "house"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.47,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{If she doesn't want to be here,\Nthen I'll just destroy it all! - OG}{She doesn't want to be here,\Nso I'll just destroy it all! - Gaijin}{I'm gonna smash it to pieces! - Polly}Dlatego właśnie zrównam je z ziemią!{Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:47.34,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gumowy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.55,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Nie pozwalaj sobie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:55.14,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Arlong Park can't ever be brought\Ndown by you inferior beings! - OG}Szumowina twojego pokroju\Nnie zdoła zniszczyć Arlong Parku!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.35,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Shark Tooth Drill! - OG}{Shark Gone... - Gaijin}Shark on...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.48,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Koło Zębatooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.52,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Topór!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.90,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{L-Look! That shock's\Ncaused Arlong Park to...! - OG}{L-Look at what that impact\Nhas done to Arlong Park! - Gaijin}C-Co za uderzenie!\NArlong Park się...!{GolDy}{Polly - NOT Gordy! Get it straight!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.95,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Impossible! It's gonna collapse! - OG}Nie może być! Rozpada się!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.58,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{This is dangerous! Everyone, get away! - OG}{This is dangerous! Everyone, get back! - Gaijin}Niedobrze! Uciekać, ale już!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.33,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Siorko Nami! Ruchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:57.62,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Ale Luffy jest w środku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.33,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Siorko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.83,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Luffy! Luffy's still...! - OG}Luffy! A co z Luffym?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.59,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.44,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:33.12,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:49.76,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Auć... Aua!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:52.43,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Co to za hałas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:58.47,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:15.28,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Arlong Park... has collapsed! - OG}Arlong Park... upadł!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.03,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Brachu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:20.66,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{What in the world happened inside? - OG}{What the hell happened inside? - Gaijin}Co tam się cholera stało?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:23.29,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{Which one won?! - OG}Kto wygrał?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:26.63,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Wszystko jest w ruinie...\NTylko nie mówcie, że...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.30,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.02,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:44.85,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,– Brachu!\N– Brachu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.61,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Na pewno nic mu nie jest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.87,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:08.96,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,{You're my friend! - OG}Jesteś jedną z nas!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.64,Main-207- PL,,0,0,0,,Tak!{OG}{I know! - Gaijin}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=47}===============================DIALOGUE============================
